{"tid":2240423,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"麵包機整麵包","createTime":"2020-10-12T15:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T21:59:39.000Z","uid":375297,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"96b3bcb2f5289736cefe2c2832bdf0319069fa40","tid":2240423,"uid":375297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>第一次整麵包，抹茶紅莓朱古力方包</ins></strong><br />\n凌晨開始整，朝早6點整完，一出爐就比屋企人切開左幾舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到個包好乾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ibd8d3J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fibd8d3J.png&h=aa17d8ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YtxH2W7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtxH2W7.png&h=60c3b577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>第二次整麵包，伯爵茶芝士粒粒方包</strong></ins><br />\n喺第二次攪拌後，拎左麵糰出黎整形狀+落芝士粒<br />\n焗之前搽左D蛋液喺面頭<br />\n出爐後攤左40分鐘，個包終於都正常少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W7oTqcJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW7oTqcJ.png&h=4676e6d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8r9HZs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8r9HZs.png&h=0616c1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4HfyqcQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4HfyqcQ.png&h=da3e30ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLMmy6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLMmy6e.png&h=4a60d17d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17f6249108e189f0e3c8457daf3b742b21fddd65","tid":2240423,"uid":376618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:41:55.000Z","msg":"想eat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aff8f9adb25eedb034a2fd907f4fc8ddc197418","tid":2240423,"uid":295855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"求普通方包食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為唔見左本說明書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4895a7332b8539509d37305b6864531b47de388b","tid":2240423,"uid":375297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8aff8f9adb25eedb034a2fd907f4fc8ddc197418","tid":2240423,"uid":295855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"求普通方包食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為唔見左本說明書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />份量係跟網上食譜<br />\n300g高筋，150g牛奶，雞蛋52g，牛油30g，酵母4g，鹽3g，糖35g（我用7g稀有糖+28g糖）"},{"pid":"b315b85d7760f21deefb6a57e061b96a7756241d","tid":2240423,"uid":295855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4895a7332b8539509d37305b6864531b47de388b","tid":2240423,"uid":375297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8aff8f9adb25eedb034a2fd907f4fc8ddc197418","tid":2240423,"uid":295855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:48:41.000Z","msg":"求普通方包食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為唔見左本說明書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />份量係跟網上食譜<br />\n300g高筋，150g牛奶，雞蛋52g，牛油30g，酵母4g，鹽3g，糖35g（我用7g稀有糖+28g糖）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T21:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />謝謝你<br />\n<br />\n之前都整得好正。但冇整一排又搵唔到個食譜。<br />\n<br />\n所以整唔番咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發覺係牛奶難搞d。<br />\n<br />\n又要新鮮又用得唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但之前用過盒裝奶又幾ok,一排4盒150ml一盒果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}